title: Little Feat Vinyl Pack 44/16
description:
Little Feat - Dixie Chicken (1975 UK K46200  Burbank label)
Little Feat - Feat's Dont Fail Me Now (1976 UK Burbank label K 56030)
Little Feat - Last Record Album (UK Original 1975 UK Release K56156)

Cleaned with Knosti machine, LAT International fluid & ionised water.
